# GitHub Workflows - {{REPO_INFRA_NAME}}

## Structure

- Workflows: `{{REPO_INFRA_NAME}}/.github/workflows/`
- Reusable actions: `{{REPO_INFRA_NAME}}/.github/actions/`
- Scripts: `{{REPO_INFRA_NAME}}/.github/scripts/`

## Conventions

- Runner: `{{INFRA_GH_RUNNER}}`
- Terraform: version via `vars.TERRAFORM_VERSION`
- Directories: `TERRAFORM_DIRECTORY`, `ENVS_DIRECTORY`, `ROOT_DIRECTORY` defined in env
- Checkout: `{{INFRA_CHECKOUT_ACTION}}`
- Setup Terraform: `hashicorp/setup-terraform@v3` with `terraform_wrapper: false`

## Custom actions

- `list-tf-layers`: generates the list of layers for matrices
- `tf-plan-layer`, `tf-destroy`: Terraform execution per layer
- `tf-replace-anchor`: replaces anchors in tfvars
- `trivy-scan`: security scan
